snippet.title: Final Project 3th Teaser
snippet.description:
this is our 3th and final teaser for our 4th Half Life (ep2) sp-mod called Final Project (FP).
FP will be released at Friday 8 Oct. 2010 on Moddb.com, Planet Phillip.com and many other game sites.
FP has 10 large sp-maps and will give you about 10 hours of gameplay, give or take.
